Description: Implements the Password-Based Key Derivation Function 2 (PBKDF2)
    according to the PKCS #5 v2.1 standard. The core implementation is derived
    from the original work by Sigfredo Ismael Nin Colón (MIT License, 2022)
    and has been packaged, refactored, and extended to better integrate with R.
